### Shopping API - Test Requests
### Execute these requests after starting the application on port 8083

### 1. Create a new shop order
POST http://localhost:8083/shopping
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userIdentifier": "user123",
  "date": "2024-01-15T10:30:00",
  "items": [
    {
      "productIdentifier": "prod001",
      "price": 29.99,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productIdentifier": "prod002",
      "price": 15.50,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ],
  "total": 75.48
}

### 2. Create another shop order
POST http://localhost:8083/shopping
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userIdentifier": "user456",
  "date": "2024-01-16T14:20:00",
  "items": [
    {
      "productIdentifier": "prod001",
      "price": 32.00,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ],
  "total": 32.00
}

### 3. Get all shops
GET http://localhost:8083/shopping

### 4. Get shop by ID (replace with actual ID from previous response)
GET http://localhost:8083/shopping/{{shopId}}

### 5. Get shops by user
GET http://localhost:8083/shopping/shopByUser?userId=user123

### 6. Get shops by date range
GET http://localhost:8083/shopping/shopByDate?dataInicio=2024-01-01&dataFim=2024-01-31

### 7. Get shops by product identifier
GET http://localhost:8083/shopping/prod001

### 8. Get shops with advanced filters (with minimum value)
GET http://localhost:8083/shopping/search?dataInicio=2024-01-01&dataFim=2024-01-31&valorMinimo=50.0

### 9. Get shops with advanced filters (without minimum value)
GET http://localhost:8083/shopping/search?dataInicio=2024-01-01&dataFim=2024-01-31

### 10. Get sales report by date
GET http://localhost:8083/shopping/report?dataInicio=2024-01-01&dataFim=2024-01-31

### 11. Test validation - Invalid shop (missing required fields)
POST http://localhost:8083/shopping
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userIdentifier": "",
  "date": "2024-01-15T10:30:00",
  "items": [
    {
      "productIdentifier": "prod001",
      "price": -10.0,
      "quantity": 0
    }
  ]
}

### 12. Test date parsing with different formats
GET http://localhost:8083/shopping/shopByDate?dataInicio=2024-01-15&dataFim=2024-01-16

### 13. Test date parsing with datetime format
GET http://localhost:8083/shopping/shopByDate?dataInicio=2024-01-15T00:00:00&dataFim=2024-01-16T23:59:59
